OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with some hazy sunshine
OL,6,Fthroughout the day. Above average
OL,7,Ftemperatures, and becoming very warm
OL,8,For hot in places. Winds breezy at
OL,9,Ftimes especially along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and settled evening,
OL,12,Fremaining cloudy for the most. The
OL,13,Fwind will ease slightly, but remaining
OL,14,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FBreezy at times with variable
OL,17,Fcloud for much of the period, staying
OL,18,Fmostly dry with hazy sunshine at
OL,19,Ftimes. Temperatures remaining above
OL,20,Faverage, and feeling very warm or hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
